text:
It's so cold outside~
I can't even feel my fingertips.

Mamimi~! Good work. Hurry up and come
over here, let's warm up by the stove together!

Ah...
So warm... I feel revived!

We can warm up together like this~! And chatting
while poking at hot pot in the kotatsu is fun too.

There are so many good things about winter~
Like oshikura manju, it's unique to winter, you know!

Oshikura manju~?
I don't do things like that~
